ABUJA – The All Progressives Congress (APC) has approved free nomination forms for all Women aspirants desirous to run on the ticket of the party in the coming 2023. The Party’s National Women Leader, Deaconess Beta Edu disclosed this Thursday at the party’s National Secretariat in Abuja. He said the endorsement has the approval of the gender-friendly APC National Working Committee NWC, led by Senator Abdullahi Adamu. Mrs Edu has there asked Nigerian women to move in en masse into the APC and run for different elective positions without intimidation, assuring them of victory at the polls. Details Later…